SHE WROTE A LETTER TO THE SCHOOL
COMPLAINING ABOUT HIM.

35:11.343 --> 35:14.646
- DO YOU HAVE A COPY
OF THAT LETTER?

35:14.646 --> 35:17.383
- NO.

