- BRETT FORRESTER.
- YEAH.

35:26.292 --> 35:28.194
SON OF A BITCH.

35:28.194 --> 35:31.563
- IS THERE ANY CHANCE
YOUR MOTHER KEPT THAT LETTER?

35:31.563 --> 35:33.799
