WITH CURT HASKINS

36:44.002 --> 36:45.737
AND SOME OTHER ALUMNI.

36:45.737 --> 36:48.307
- YEAH. I STILL DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU WERE DOING THERE.

36:52.911 --> 36:56.014
- WE'RE INVESTIGATING
SEXUAL ASSAULTS AT YOUR SCHOOL.

36:56.014 --> 36:58.584
ONE NAME CAME UP
AFTER YOU LEFT.

36:58.584 --> 37:00.886
- ONE OF YOUR OLD TEACHERS.
MR. STREPEK.

37:00.886 --> 37:02.888
- I TOLD THEM WHAT YOU TOLD ME

37:02.888 --> 37:05.023
