FALSELY ACCUSED.

37:05.023 --> 37:07.025
- CAN YOU TELL US, NATHAN?

37:07.025 --> 37:09.928
- I DON'T REALLY REMEMBER.

37:09.928 --> 37:12.864
- BUT WE HEARD HE SEXUALLY
