37:38.590 --> 37:39.925
- WHAT DO YOU DO, NATHAN?

37:39.925 --> 37:42.027
- I--[ahem].

37:42.027 --> 37:44.330
BEEN WRITING SOME SONGS.
- NICE.

37:44.330 --> 37:46.532
CAN WE HEAR THEM ANYWHERE?

37:46.532 --> 37:49.000
- I HAVEN'T...
PUBLISHED THEM YET.

37:49.000 --> 37:50.836
- I'LL INVITE YOU
TO THE FIRST CONCERT.

37:50.836 --> 37:52.938
LEAVE. NOW.
WE'RE DONE.

37:52.938 --> 37:54.806
- NOT QUITE.

37:54.806 --> 37:56.642
YOU KNOW, WHEN WE FIRST MET,
MR. FORRESTER,

37:56.642 --> 38:00.879
YOU TOLD US THAT SOME PEOPLE
LIVE DISAPPOINTING LIVES.

38:00.879 --> 38:03.649
- AND?
- ARE YOU DISAPPOINTED?

38:03.649 --> 38:06.585
THAT NATHAN DIDN'T JOIN
THE FAMILY FIRM,

38:06.585 --> 38:08.887
THAT HE WRITES SONGS
HERE IN YOUR HOUSE

38:08.887 --> 38:10.822
THAT NOBODY WILL SING?

38:12.758 --> 38:17.363
- I REALLY DON'T SEE HOW
THAT'S ANY OF YOUR CONCERN.

38:17.363 --> 38:19.064
- IT IS IF IT HAS TO DO
WITH BENJAMIN STREPEK.

38:19.064 --> 38:21.600
- HE'S ALREADY TOLD YOU

38:21.600 --> 38:25.737
