38:39.351 --> 38:42.588
- AND WHAT, DAD?

38:42.588 --> 38:44.022
NO, YOU'RE RIGHT, DAD.

38:44.022 --> 38:46.758
MUST SAVE THE GOOD NAME
OF MANOR HILL.

38:46.758 --> 38:49.928
- THAT SCHOOL.
MANOR HILL.

38:49.928 --> 38:52.531
THAT'S ALL YOUR FATHER
